<h3 id="more-information">More Information</h3>

<p>Facebook removed the checkin end point as of Graph API version 2.0. Checkins have been depreciated in favor of attaching place information to posts, or tagging places in Open Graph stories.</p>

<p>So, to checkin, you now need to tag a place in your Open Graph story.</p>

<p><strong>Facebook donâ€™t allow you to force like pages any more</strong>. Itâ€™s not a good way to encourage usage.</p>

<p>If you have a specific requirement other than the publish_action, please get in touch and we can discuss adding more features to CT.</p>

<p>Enjoy! Remember, if you donâ€™t want to do all this, you can use our application. Itâ€™s all set up for you.</p>

